'''天箭座'''是昏暗但独特的北天[[星座|星座]]，原名“{{lang|la|Sagitta}}”是[[拉丁语|拉丁语]]，意为箭。天箭座属于二世纪天文学家[[克劳狄乌斯·托勒密|克劳狄乌斯·托勒密]]所列48个星座，也属[[國際天文聯會|國際天文聯會]]定义的[[星座列表|88个现代星座]]。天箭座历史久远，但所有恒星亮度都不超过[[视星等|第三等]]，面积在88个星座中倒数第三。

3.47视星等的[[左旗五|左旗五]]是天箭座最亮恒星，质量约为太阳九成，但已进入老化的[[紅巨星|紅巨星]]时期，直径达太阳54倍。[[左旗三|左旗三]]、[[左旗增一|左旗增一]]、[[左旗四|左旗四]]和[[天箭座θ|天箭座θ]]都是[[恆星系統|恆星系統]]，可以用小型望远镜看到内部组成。[[天箭座V|天箭座V]]是[[激變變星|激變變星]]，即[[白矮星|白矮星]]吸积[[洛希瓣|捐助恒星]]形成的[[聯星|聯星]]系统，预计会在2083年左右发展成[[新星|新星]]并短暂成为[[银河系|银河系]][[光度|光度]]最高的恒星，也是天空中非常明亮的星体。天箭座有两个恒星系统拥有类木星行星，另外[[天箭座15|天箭座15]]还有[[棕矮星|棕矮星]]伴星。

== 历史 ==
[[File:Sidney_Hall_-_Urania's_Mirror_-_Delphinus,_Sagitta,_Aquila,_and_Antinous.jpg|thumb]]上方]]

[[古典希臘時期|古希腊人]]称天箭座“奥斯托斯”（{{lang|el|Oistos}}），意为“箭”<ref name="Kunitzsch" />，属于[[克劳狄乌斯·托勒密|克劳狄乌斯·托勒密]]所列的48个星座<ref name="ridpathsag">{{cite web | archive-date = 2020-08-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200806203934/http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/sagitta.htm | dead-url = no | url = http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/sagitta.html | title = Sagitta | last = Ridpath | first = Ian | work = Star Tales | access-date = 2020-11-29 }}</ref>。相传[[朱庇特|朱庇特]]每天派老鹰（即[[天鹰座|天鹰座]]）啄食[[普罗米修斯|普罗米修斯]]的肝脏，[[赫丘利|赫拉克勒斯]]用来击杀老鹰的箭便是天箭座<ref name="hyginus_14">{{cite web | archive-date = 2020-11-27 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127014310/https://www.theoi.com/Text/HyginusAstronomica.html#15 | url = https://www.theoi.com/Text/HyginusAstronomica.html#15 | title = Astronomica | author = Hyginus | translator = Mary Grant | website = Theoi Project | accessdate = 2020-11-29 }}</ref>。天箭座位于天鹰座北面边界以外，业余[[博学家|博学家]]理查德·欣克利·艾伦（{{lang|en|Richard Hinckley Allen}}）提议用天箭座代表赫拉克勒斯射向附近[[斯廷法利斯湖怪鸟|斯廷法利斯湖怪鸟]]的箭（[[赫拉克勒斯的十二伟业|赫拉克勒斯的第六项伟业]]），这种怪鸟的爪子、喙和翅膀都是钢铁，在[[阿卡迪亞州|阿卡迪亞州]]沼泽吃人为生。天箭座与天鹰座、[[天鹅座|天鹅座]]和[[天琴座|天琴座]]相邻，中间隔着赫库利阿（{{lang|en|Herculea}}）。<ref>{{cite book | first = Richard Hinckley | last = Allen | title = Star-Names and Their Meanings | pages = 349–351 | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-486-21079-7 | access-date = 2020-11-29 | url = https://www.google.com/books/edition/Star_Names/l8V2DY3tQMgC?hl=en&gbpv=1&dq=Star-Names+and+Their+Meanings&printsec=frontcover | year = 1963 | origyear = 1899 | publisher = Dover Publications | archive-date = 2021-04-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210428075738/https://www.google.com/books/edition/Star_Names/l8V2DY3tQMgC?hl=en&gbpv=1&dq=Star-Names+and+Their+Meanings&printsec=frontcover }}</ref>希腊学者[[埃拉托斯特尼|埃拉托斯特尼]]声称，天箭座代表[[阿波罗|阿波罗]]消灭[[独眼巨人|独眼巨人]]的箭<ref name="hyginus_14" />。罗马人为星座起名“{{lang|la|Sagitta}}”（拉丁语“天箭座”）<ref>{{Cite book | title = The Star Atlas Companion : What You Need to Know about the Constellations | url = https://archive.org/details/staratlascompani00bagn | last = Bagnall | first = Philip M. | year = 2012 | publisher = [[施普林格科学+商业媒体|Springer]] | pages = [https://archive.org/details/staratlascompani00bagn/page/386 386]–389 | location = New York | isbn = 9781461408307 | oclc = 794225463}}</ref>。阿拉伯人称其为“al-sahm”，同样是箭的意思，后来误传成“Sham”，专指恒星[[左旗一|左旗一]]。希腊语名“{{lang|el|Oistos}}”曾误译成“{{lang|el-latn|ὁ istos}}”，意为“织机”，所以阿拉伯语也跟着误解为“al-nawl”，此外还称“al-'anaza”，意为“长矛”或“标枪”。<ref name="Kunitzsch" />

== 简介 ==
天箭座四颗最亮的恒星组成箭形[[星群|星群]]，位于明亮的[[河鼓二|牛郎星]]北面<ref name="moore366">{{Cite book | title = The Observer's Year: 366 Nights in the Universe | url = https://archive.org/details/observersyearnig00moor_834 | last = Moore | first = Patrick | page = [https://archive.org/details/observersyearnig00moor_834/page/n64 10] | year = 2005 | isbn = 978-1-85233-884-8 | publisher = [[施普林格科学+商业媒体|Springer Science & Business Media]] | location = New York}}</ref>，星座面积仅79.9平方度，占天空0.194%，在[[星座列表|88个现代星座]]中排第86，只比[[小马座|小马座]]和[[南十字座|南十字座]]大<ref name="tirionconst" />。北半球每年春末到秋初很容易看到天箭座，午夜[[中天_(天文學)|中天]]是7月17日<ref name="thompson2">{{cite book | title = Illustrated Guide to Astronomical Wonders: From Novice to Master Observer | last1 = Thompson | first1 = Robert Bruce | author2 = Barbara Fritchman | location = Sebastopol, California | year = 2007 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=ymt9nj_uPhwC&pg=PA392%7Cpage%3D392%7Cisbn%3D978-0-596-52685-6&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | publisher = O'Reilly Media, Inc. | accessdate = 2020-11-29 | archive-date = 2021-08-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210806053749/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=ymt9nj_uPhwC&pg=PA392%7Cpage%3D392%7Cisbn%3D978-0-596-52685-6&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false }}</ref>。受位置影响，只有[[南緯69度線|南緯69度線]]以北能看到整个[[星座|星座]]<ref name="tirionconst" />{{refn|group="注"|从技术角度而言，天箭座部分位置会出现在[[南緯69度線|南纬69度]]和[[南緯73度線|73度线]]之间的地面线上方，但只高于地平线几度的恒星无论通过何等手段都无法观测<ref name="tirionconst" />。}}天箭座北靠[[狐狸座|狐狸座]]，西临[[武仙座|武仙座]]，南挨天鹰座，东接[[海豚座|海豚座]]。1922年，国际天文联会确定以三字母缩写“{{lang|en|Sge}}”代指天箭座；星座拉丁语名没有字母“{{lang|en|e}}”，为避免和[[人马座|人马座]]混淆，人马座的拉丁语名“{{lang|la|Sagittarius}}”和属格“{{lang|la|Sagittarii}}”都不含“{{lang|en|e}}”，故而设计缩写代码的美国天文学家[[亨利·诺利斯·罗素|亨利·诺利斯·罗素]]从天箭座名称[[属格|属格]]“{{lang|la|Sagittae}}”中挑出字母“{{lang|en|e}}”<ref name="pa30_469" />。1930年，[[尤金·德爾波特|尤金·德爾波特]]正式划分星座边界，形成有12条[[邊_(幾何)|边]]的多边形（见文首信息框）。根据[[赤道坐標系統|赤道坐標系統]]，星座[[赤经|赤经]]位于{{RA|18|57.2}}和{{RA|20|20.5}}之间，[[赤纬|赤纬]]位于16.08°到21.64°之间。<ref name="boundary" />

== 显著特点 ==
=== 恒星 ===
{{see also|天箭座恒星列表}}
天体制图师[[約翰·拜耳|約翰·拜耳]]用[[拜耳命名法|拜耳命名法]]为天箭座八颗恒星命名，即“[[Α|Α]]”至“[[Θ|Θ]]”八个字母。英格兰天文学家[[約翰·佛蘭斯蒂德|約翰·佛蘭斯蒂德]]用字母“{{lang|en|x}}”（误写成“[[Χ|Χ]]”）、“{{lang|en|y}}”和“{{lang|en|z}}”分别代表天箭座13、14和15，但不为后世天文学家[[约翰·贝维斯|约翰·贝维斯]]和[[弗朗西斯·贝利|弗朗西斯·贝利]]接受。<ref name="wagman">{{cite book | last = Wagman | first = Morton | year = 2003 | title = Lost Stars: Lost, Missing and Troublesome Stars from the Catalogues of Johannes Bayer, Nicholas Louis de Lacaille, John Flamsteed, and Sundry Others | pages = 266–267, 515 | publisher = The McDonald & Woodward Publishing Company | location = Blacksburg, Virginia | isbn = 978-0-939923-78-6}}</ref>

==== 明亮恒星 ====
托勒密把最亮的[[左旗五|左旗五]]标为箭头<ref name="ridpathsag" />，拜耳认为左旗五、[[左旗增廿六|左旗增廿六]]、天箭座θ组成箭形<ref name="wagman" />。左旗五是3.47视星等、光谱等级{{lang|en|M0 III}}的[[紅巨星|紅巨星]]<ref name="strassmeier">{{cite journal | bibcode = 2018A&A...612A..45S | title = PEPSI deep spectra. II. Gaia benchmark stars and other M-K standards | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 612 | pages = A45 | last1 = Strassmeier | first1 = K. G. | last2 = Ilyin | first2 = I. | last3 = Weber | first3 = M. | year = 2018 | arxiv = 1712.06967 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/201731633}}</ref>，距地球258±4光年<ref name="vanLeeuwen2007">{{cite journal | first = F. | last = van Leeuwen | title = Validation of the New Hipparcos Reduction | journal = [[天文与天体物理学报|Astronomy and Astrophysics]] | volume = 474 | issue = 2 | pages = 653–664 | year = 2007 | bibcode = 2007A&A...474..653V | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20078357 | arxiv = 0708.1752}}</ref>，质量约占太阳九成，但半径是太阳的54倍，亮度575倍，很可能已进入[[恆星演化|恆星演化]]的[[紅巨星分支|紅巨星分支]]，核心的氢已经耗尽，正消耗核心周围的氢<ref name="stock">{{cite journal | bibcode = 2018A&A...616A..33S | title = Precise radial velocities of giant stars. X. Bayesian stellar parameters and evolutionary stages for 372 giant stars from the Lick planet search | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 616 | pages = A33 | last1 = Stock | first1 = Stephan | last2 = Reffert | first2 = Sabine | last3 = Quirrenbach | first3 = Andreas | last4 = Hauschildt | first4 = P. | year = 2018 | arxiv = 1805.04094 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/201833111}}</ref>。

[[左旗三|左旗三]]是天箭座第二亮的恒星，属于联星，拜尔认为左旗三和左旗增一组成箭尖<ref name="wagman" />。左旗三包含3.9倍太阳质量、152倍太阳直径、光谱等级{{lang|en|M2 II}}的[[紅超巨星|紅超巨星]]和2.9倍太阳质量的蓝白[[主序星|主序星]]，两者相互围绕旋转，轨道周期十年<ref name="Eaton">{{cite journal | title = Winds and accretion in delta Sagittae | last1 = Eaton | first1 = Joel A. | last2 = Hartkopf | first2 = William I. | last3 = McAlister | first3 = Harold A. | last4 = Mason | first4 = Brian D. | journal = [[天文期刊|Astronomical Journal]] | volume = 109 | number = 4 | pages = 1856–1866 | year = 1995 | bibcode = 1995AJ....109.1856E | doi = 10.1086/117412}}</ref>。左旗增一是三星系统，距地球约326光年，主星属[[A型主序星|A型主序星]]<ref name="Eggleton2008">{{cite journal | last1 = Eggleton | first1 = P. P. | last2 = Tokovinin | first2 = A. A. | title = A catalogue of multiplicity among bright stellar systems | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | volume = 389 | issue = 2 | pages = 869–879 | date = 2008-09 | bibcode = 2008MNRAS.389..869E | doi=10.1111/j.1365-2966.2008.13596.x | arxiv = 0806.2878}}</ref>。

拜尔的《测天图》把左旗一、[[左旗二|左旗二]]和左旗增一绘成箭的羽毛<ref name="wagman" />。左旗一是4.38[[视星等|视星等]]、光谱等级{{lang|en|G1 II}}的黄色[[亮巨星|亮巨星]]，距地球382±8光年<ref name="Gaia-DR2alpha">{{cite DR2|1824277055360974720}}</ref>。它拥有四倍太阳质量，已经大幅膨胀并增亮，直径是太阳20倍，[[光度|光度]]340倍<ref name="kalersham">{{cite web | first = James B. | last = Kaler | title = Sham | work = Stars | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200919162226/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/sham.html | publisher = University of Illinois | url = http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/sham.html | accessdate = 2020-11-29 | archive-date = 2020-09-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。左旗二的视星等和左旗一相同，是距地球420±10光年的{{lang|en|G}}型[[巨星|巨星]]<ref name="Gaia-DR2beta">{{cite DR2|1823991938300446336}}</ref>，估计已有约1.29亿年历史，拥有4.33倍太阳质量<ref name="Liu2014">{{cite journal | title = The Lithium Abundances of a Large Sample of Red Giants | display-authors = 1 | last1 = Liu | first1 = Y. J. | last2 = Tan | first2 = K. F. | last3 = Wang | first3 = L. | last4 = Zhao | first4 = G. | last5 = Sato | first5 = Bun'ei | last6 = Takeda | first6 = Y. | last7 = Li | first7 = H. N. | journal = [[天文物理期刊|The Astrophysical Journal]] | arxiv = 1404.1687 | volume = 785 | issue = 2 | id = 94 | page = 12 | year = 2014 | doi = 10.1088/0004-637X/785/2/94 | bibcode = 2014ApJ...785...94L}}</ref>，已经扩大到原有直径的约27倍<ref name="vanBelle2009">{{cite journal | title = Supergiant temperatures and linear radii from near-infrared interferometry | journal = [[皇家天文學會月報|Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society]] | volume = 394 | issue = 4 | page = 1925 | year = 2009 | last1 = Van Belle | first1 = G. T. | last2 = Creech-Eakman | first2 = M. J. | last3 = Hart | first3 = A. | bibcode = 2009MNRAS.394.1925V | arxiv = 0811.4239 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2008.14146.x}}</ref>。左旗增一是[[双星|双星]]，其组成可用小型望远镜观测<ref name="turnleft">{{cite book | last = Consolmagno | first = Guy | title = Turn Left at Orion: Hundreds of Night Sky Objects to See in a Home Telescope – and How to Find Them | publisher = [[劍橋大學出版社|Cambridge University Press]] | location = Cambridge, United Kingdom | year = 2019 | origyear = 1989 | page = 138 | isbn = 978-1-108-45756-9 | accessdate = 2020-11-29 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=D2JjDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA139&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | archive-date = 2021-08-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210806063535/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=D2JjDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA139&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false }}</ref>。其中5.77视星等的主星<ref name="Mason2014" />约有3.31亿年历史，是光谱等级{{lang|en|G8 III}}的黄巨星，质量是太阳3.09倍<ref name="takeda14">{{cite journal | title = Spectroscopic study on the beryllium abundances of red giant stars | journal = Publications of the Astronomical Society of Japan | volume = 66 | issue = 5 | pages = 91 | year = 2014 | last1 = Takeda | first1 = Yoichi | last2 = Tajitsu | first2 = Akito | doi = 10.1093/pasj/psu066 | bibcode = 2014PASJ...66...91T | arxiv = 1406.7066}}</ref>，已膨胀到原有直径的{{val|18.37|0.65|0.88}}倍<ref name="GaiaDR2epsilon" />，距地球580±10光年<ref name="GaiaDR2epsilon">{{Cite DR2|4321830946398475776}}</ref>。8.35视星等的伴星距主星87.4[[角秒|角秒]]<ref name="Mason2014">{{cite journal | last1 = Mason | first1 = B. D. | last2 = Wycoff | first2 = G. L. | last3 = Hartkopf | first3 = W. I. | last4 = Douglass | first4 = G. G. | last5 = Worley | first5 = C. E. | title = The Washington Visual Double Star Catalog | journal = [[自然_(期刊)|Nature]] | year = 2014 | volume = 122 | issue = 6 | page = 3466 | bibcode = 2001AJ....122.3466M | doi = 10.1086/323920}}</ref>，但实际上是与主星无关、离地球七千光年的[[藍超巨星|藍超巨星]]<ref name="GaiaDR2comp">{{cite DR2|4321830980758181760}}</ref>。

左旗增廿六是5.1视星等、光谱等级{{lang|en|K2 III}}的橙巨星，距地球155.9±0.9光年，有61.1%的几率属[[畢宿星團|毕宿]]-[[昴宿星團|昴宿星團]]，[[恆星運動學|运动方向相同]]<ref name="Famaey2005">{{cite journal | last1 = Famaey | first1 = B. | last2 = Jorissen | first2 = A. | last3 = Luri | first3 = X. | last4 = Mayor | first4 = M. | last5 = Udry | first5 = S. | last6 = Dejonghe | first6 = H. | last7 = Turon | first7 = C. | title = Local kinematics of K and M giants from CORAVEL/Hipparcos/Tycho-2 data. Revisiting the concept of superclusters | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 430 | pages = 165–186 | year = 2005 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20041272 | bibcode = 2005A&A...430..165F | arxiv = astro-ph/0409579}}</ref>。天箭座θ是联星，两星相距12角秒，可用小型望远镜观测<ref name="turnleft" />。其中偏亮的为6.5视星等，是光谱等级{{lang|en|F3 V}}的黄白主序星<ref name="abt1985">{{cite journal | last = Abt | first = Helmut A. | title = Visual multiples. VIII. 1000 MK types | journal = Astrophysical Journal, Supplementary Series | year = 1985 | bibcode = 1985ApJS...59...95A | volume = 59 | pages = 95–112 | doi = 10.1086/191064}}</ref>，离地球146.1±0.2光年<ref name="Gaia-DR2tet1">{{cite DR2|1829590548393010560}}</ref>。另一颗是8.8视星等的主序星，光谱等级{{lang|en|G5 V}}。此外，距天箭座θ91角秒还有7.4视星等的橙巨星，光谱等级{{lang|en|K2 III}}<ref name="abt1985" />，距地球842±9光年<ref name="Gaia-DR2tet2">{{cite DR2|1829590410954063744}}</ref>。

==== 变星 ====
变星是业余天文学家的热门目标，他们的观测对人类理解恒星行为贡献很大<ref>{{cite web | last = Tooke | first = Owen | title = Variables: What Are They and Why Observe Them? | accessdate = 2020-11-29 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201023214851/https://www.aavso.org/variables-what-are-they-why-observe-them | url = https://www.aavso.org/variables-what-are-they-why-observe-them | publisher = AAVSO | date = 2017-08-24 | archive-date = 2020-10-23 }}</ref>。[[天箭座R|天箭座R]]是罕见的[[金牛座RV型變星|金牛座RV型變星]]，视星等在8.2至10.4范围变化<ref name="Levy 1998">{{cite book | last = Levy | first = David H. | title = Observing Variable Stars: A Guide for the Beginner | publisher = [[劍橋大學出版社|Cambridge University Press]] | location = Cambridge, United Kingdom | date = 1998 | pages = 152–153 | isbn = 978-0-521-62755-9 | access-date = 2020-11-29 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=5-O2cd937FMC&pg=PA153&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | archive-date = 2020-12-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201210041027/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=5-O2cd937FMC&pg=PA153&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>，距地球约8100光年<ref name="dr2R">{{cite DR2|1808748613981554176}}</ref>，直径是太阳的{{val|61.2|12.4|9.9}}倍，光度{{val|2,329|744|638|fmt=commas}}倍，但质量很可能比太阳小。天箭座{{lang|en|R}}已进入老年期，源自恒星演化的[[漸近巨星支|漸近巨星支]]，正朝[[行星状星云|行星状星云]]发展<ref name="bodikiss">{{cite journal | doi = 10.3847/1538-4357/aafc24 | title = Physical Properties of Galactic RV Tauri Stars from Gaia DR2 Data | journal = [[天文物理期刊|The Astrophysical Journal]] | volume = 872 | issue = 1 | pages = 60 | year = 2019 | last1 = Bódi | first1 = A. | last2 = Kiss | first2 = L. L. | bibcode = 2019ApJ...872...60B | arxiv = 1901.01409}}</ref>。[[天箭座FG|天箭座FG]]是光度很高的“重生”恒星，距地球约四千光年<ref name="dr2FG">{{cite DR2|1828750899461025536}}</ref>。该星是在变成白矮星前启动氦壳聚变反应，接下来先扩张成蓝超巨星，然后在不到一个世纪前发展成{{lang|en|K}}级[[超巨星|超巨星]]<ref name="jurcsik1999">{{cite journal | bibcode = 1999NewAR..43..415J | title = The remarkable evolution of the post-AGB star FG Sge | last1 = Jurcsik | first1 = Johanna | last2 = Montesinos | first2 = Benjamín. | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180719102044/http://real.mtak.hu/2086/1/K.pdf | journal = New Astronomy Reviews | year = 1999 | volume = 43 | issue = 6 | page = 415 | doi = 10.1016/S1387-6473(99)00098-6 | dead-url = no | url = http://real.mtak.hu/2086/1/K.pdf | archive-date = 2018-07-19 | access-date = 2020-11-29 }}</ref>，周围是天箭座{{lang|en|FG}}脱离漸近巨星支时形成的微弱行星状星云“海因兹1–5”<ref name="rosenbush2015">{{cite journal | bibcode = 2015Ap.....58...46R | title = Photometry, Spectrometry, and Polarimetry of FG Sge in the Active State | last1 = Rosenbush | first1 = A. É. | last2 = Efimov | first2 = Yu. S. | journal = Astrophysics | year = 2015 | volume = 58 | issue = 1 | page = 46 | doi = 10.1007/s10511-015-9365-x }}</ref>。

[[天箭座S|天箭座S]]是[[經典造父變星|經典造父變星]]，视星等在5.24至6.04间以8.38天为周期变动，也是光谱等级在{{lang|en|F6 Ib}}和{{lang|en|G5 Ib}}间脉动的黄白超巨星<ref name="AAVSOS">{{cite web | archivedate = 2020-10-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201003025859/http://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=27343 | url = https://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=27343 | title = S Sagittae | last = Watson | first = Christopher | date = 2010-01-04 | publisher = AAVSO | accessdate = 2020-11-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，质量是太阳的六到七倍，光度3500倍<ref name="kalerSSge">{{cite web | first = James B. | last = Kaler | title = S Sagittae | work = Stars | publisher = University of Illinois | url = http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/ssge.html | date = 2013-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200919163441/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/ssge.html | archive-date = 2020-09-19 | accessdate = 2020-11-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，距地球约5100光年<ref name="Gaia-DR2S">{{cite DR2|1820309639468685824}}</ref>。[[HD_183143|HD 183143]]距地球约7900光年，是高光度<ref name="dr2">{{cite DR2|4323280515006629760}}</ref>蓝[[特超巨星|特超巨星]]<ref name="chentsov">{{cite journal | last1 = Chentsov | first1 = E. L. | title = HD 183143: A Hypergiant | journal = Astronomy Letters | volume = 30 | issue = 5 | year = 2004 | pages = 325–331 | doi = 10.1134/1.1738155 | bibcode = 2004AstL...30..325C}}</ref>，其光谱中还发现离子化的[[巴克明斯特富勒烯|巴克明斯特富勒烯]]分子[[红外线|红外线]]带<ref name="c60">{{cite journal | bibcode = 2015ApJ...812L...8W | arxiv = 1509.06818 | title = Identification of More Interstellar C60+ Bands | journal = The Astrophysical Journal Letters | volume = 812 | pages = L8 | last1 = Walker | first1 = G. A. H. | last2 = Bohlender | first2 = D. A. | last3 = Maier | first3 = J. P. | last4 = Campbell | first4 = E. K. | year = 2015 | issue = 1 | doi = 10.1088/2041-8205/812/1/L8}}</ref>。[[WR_124|WR 124]]是高速移动的[[沃爾夫–拉葉星|沃爾夫–拉葉星]]，周围是喷射气体组成的星云<ref name="crowther">{{cite journal | bibcode = 1999A&A...350.1007C | title = Wolf–Rayet nebulae as tracers of stellar ionizing fluxes. I. M1-67 | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 350 | pages = 1007 | last1 = Crowther | first1 = Paul A. | last2 = Pasquali | first2 = A. | last3 = De Marco | first3 = Orsola | last4 = Schmutz | first4 = W. | last5 = Hillier | first5 = D. J. | last6 = De Koter | first6 = A. | year = 1999 | arxiv = astro-ph/9908200}}</ref>。

天箭座{{lang|en|U}}是黯淡的联星，视星等以3.4天为周期在6.6至9.2范围变动，是天文爱好者使用小型望远镜观测的理想目标<ref name="moore366" />。联星包含两颗星，其一是光谱等级{{lang|en|B8 V}}的蓝白星，另一颗是老化恒星，已经冷却并膨胀成光谱等级{{lang|en|G4 III-IV}}的黄[[次巨星|次巨星]]。两星相互绕行且距离很近，次巨星已经膨胀到超出[[洛希瓣|洛希瓣]]范围，物质由温度更高的蓝白星吸收，故属半分离联星。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Malkov | first1 = Oleg Yu | title = Semidetached double-lined eclipsing binaries: Stellar parameters and rare classes | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | year = 2020 | volume = 491 | issue = 4 | pages = 5489–5497 | bibcode = 2020MNRAS.491.5489M | doi = 10.1093/mnras/stz3363}}</ref>天箭座{{lang|en|U}}距地球900±10光年<ref name="Gaia-DR2u">{{cite DR2|4516549576568929408}}</ref>，附近还有[[半規則變星|半規則變星]]天箭座{{lang|en|X}}，视星等以196年天周期在7.9至8.4范围变化<ref name="moore366" />。天箭座{{lang|en|X}}是[[碳星|碳星]]，表面温度约2576{{lang|en|K}}<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Taranova | first1 = O.G. | first2 = V. I. | last2 = Shenavrin | title = JHKLM Photometry for Carbon Stars | journal = Astronomy Letters | year = 2004 | volume = 30 | issue = 8 | pages = 605–622 | doi = 10.1134/1.1784497 | bibcode = 2004AstL...30..549T}}</ref>。

天箭座18附近的[[天箭座V|天箭座V]]是[[超軟X射線源|天箭座V变星]]的原型，即属超軟X射線源的[[激變變星|激變變星]]<ref name="Levy 1998" />。预料其中的两颗恒星会在2083年左右融合成[[亮紅新星|亮紅新星]]，短暂成为[[银河系|银河系]]光度最高的星，也是天上非常亮的恒星<ref name="2020-01">{{Cite web | date = 2020-01-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201101092810/https://phys.org/news/2020-01-binary-star-sagittae-bright-nova.html | url = https://phys.org/news/2020-01-binary-star-sagittae-bright-nova.html | title = Binary star V Sagittae to explode as very bright nova by century's end | last = Lavalle | first = Mimi | website = phys.org | access-date = 2020-11-29 | archivedate = 2020-11-01 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | title = There will be a new brightest star in the sky, when it explodes in about 60 years | url = https://www.cnn.com/2020/01/08/world/binary-star-saggitae-explosion-scn/index.html | publisher = CNN | access-date = 2020-11-29 | date = 2020-01-08 | author = Ashley Strickland | archivedate = 2020-06-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200610210332/https://www.cnn.com/2020/01/08/world/binary-star-saggitae-explosion-scn/index.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[天箭座WZ|天箭座WZ]]同样是激变变星，包括八成五太阳质量的[[白矮星|白矮星]]和经计算仅8%太阳质量、光谱等级{{lang|en|L2}}的[[棕矮星|棕矮星]]<ref name="apj667">{{cite journal | last1 = Steeghs | first1 = Danny | last2 = Howell | first2 = Steve B. | last3 = Knigge | first3 = Christian | last4 = Gänsicke | first4 = Boris T. | last5 = Sion | first5 = Edward M. | last6 = Welsh | first6 = William F. | title = Dynamical Constraints on the Component Masses of the Cataclysmic Variable WZ Sagittae | journal = [[天文物理期刊|The Astrophysical Journal]] | volume = 667 | issue = 1 | pages = 442–447 | date = 2007-09 | doi = 10.1086/520702 | bibcode = 2007ApJ...667..442S | arxiv = 0706.0987}}</ref>。天箭座{{lang|en|WZ}}绝大部分时间是视星等不足15的黯淡星体，曾于1913、1946和1978年爆发至可用双筒望远镜观察<ref name="moore366" />。[[黑寡婦脈衝星|黑寡婦脈衝星]]（B1957+20）是人类发现的第二颗[[毫秒脈衝星|毫秒脈衝星]]<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Fruchter | first1 = A. S. | last2 = Stinebring | first2 = D. R. | last3 = Taylor | first3 = J. H. | year = 1988 | title = A millisecond pulsar in an eclipsing binary | journal = [[自然_(期刊)|Nature]] | volume = 333 | issue = 6170 | pages = 237–239 | bibcode = 1988Natur.333..237F | doi = 10.1038/333237a0}}</ref>。质量极大的[[中子星|中子星]][[燒蝕|燒蝕]]棕矮星伴星，导致脉冲星的无线电信号在穿过外流物质期间衰减<ref>{{Cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018112831/https://chandra.harvard.edu/photo/2003/b1957/ | dead-url = no | url = https://chandra.harvard.edu/photo/2003/b1957/ | title = B1957+20: A Cocoon Found Inside the Black Widow's Web | website = Chandra | access-date = 2020-11-29 | archive-date = 2020-10-18 }}</ref>。

==== 拥有系外行星的恒星 ====
[[File:Messier_71_Hubble_WikiSky.jpg|thumb]]球状星团]]

[[HD_231701|HD 231701]]是温度和尺寸都超过太阳的[[黃-白矮星|黄白主序星]]，2007年人类用[[系外行星偵測法|径向速度法]]发现它拥有类[[木星|木星]]行星，行星距恒星0.57[[天文单位|天文单位]]，公转周期141.6天<ref name="Fischer2007">{{cite journal | title = Five Intermediate-Period Planets from the N2K Sample | last1 = Fischer | first1 = Debra A. | last2 = Vogt | first2 = Steven S. | last3 = Marcy | first3 = Geoffrey W. | last4 = Butler | first4 = R. Paul | last5 = Sato | first5 = Bun’ei | last6 = Henry | first6 = Gregory W. | last7 = Robinson | first7 = Sarah | last8 = Laughlin | first8 = Gregory | last9 = Ida | first9 = Shigeru | journal = [[天文物理期刊|The Astrophysical Journal]] | volume = 669 | issue = 2 | pages = 1336–1344 | year = 2007 | arxiv = 0704.1191 | bibcode = 2007ApJ...669.1336F | doi = 10.1086/521869}}</ref>。{{lang|en|HAT-P}}-34的质量是太阳{{val|1.392|0.047}}倍，直径{{val|1.535|0.135|0.102}}倍，光度{{val|3.63|0.75|0.51}}倍，视星等10.4<ref name="Bakos2012" />，距地球819±9光年<ref name="Gaia-DR2hat34">{{cite DR2|1810218734055374720}}</ref>。2012年，人类发现质量为木星{{val|3.328|0.211}}倍的行星在该恒星附近掠过，公转周期5.45天，两者相距0.06天文单位，估计行星表面温度是1,520±60K<ref name="Bakos2012">{{cite journal | title = HAT-P-34b – HAT-P-37b: Four Transiting Planets More Massive Than Jupiter Orbiting Moderately Bright Stars | last1 = Bakos | first1 = G. Á. | last2 = Hartman | first2 = J. D. | last3 = Torres | first3 = G. | last4 = Béky | first4 = B. | last5 = Latham | first5 = D. W. | last6 = Buchhave | first6 = L. A. | last7 = Csubry | first7 = Z. | last8 = Kovács | first8 = Géza | last9 = Bieryla | first9 = A. | last10 = Quinn | first10 = S. | last11 = Szklenár | first11 = T. | last12 = Esquerdo | first12 = G. A. | last13 = Shporer | first13 = A. | last14 = Noyes | first14 = R. W. | last15 = Fischer | first15 = D. A. | last16 = Johnson | first16 = J. A. | last17 = Howard | first17 = A. W. | last18 = Marcy | first18 = G. W. | last19 = Sato | first19 = B. | last20 = Penev | first20 = K. | last21 = Everett | first21 = M. | last22 = Sasselov | first22 = D. D. | last23 = Fűrész | first23 = G. | last24 = Stefanik | first24 = R. P. | last25 = Lázár | first25 = J. | last26 = Papp | first26 = I. | last27 = Sári | first27 = P. | journal = [[天文期刊|The Astronomical Journal]] | volume = 144 | issue = 1 | pages = 19–32 | year = 2012 | arxiv = 1201.0659 | bibcode = 2012AJ....144...19B | doi = 10.1088/0004-6256/144/1/19}}</ref>。[[天箭座15|天箭座15]]是类太阳恒星，质量、半径和光度分别是太阳的{{val|1.08|0.04}}、{{val|1.115|0.021}}和{{val|1.338|0.03}}倍。它的棕矮星伴星尺寸接近木星，但质量是木星69倍，表面温度在1510至1850K范围，公转周期约73.3年。估计该系统已有25±18亿年历史。<ref name="Crepp2012">{{cite journal | last1 = Crepp | first = Justin R. | last2 = Johnson | first2 = John Asher | last3 = Fischer | first3 = Debra A. | last4 = Howard | first4 = Andrew W. | last5 = Marcy | first5 = Geoffrey W. | last6 = Wright | first6 = Jason T. | last7 = Isaacson | first7 = Howard | last8 = Boyajian | first8 = Tabetha | last9 = von Braun | first9 = Kaspar | last10 = Hillenbrand | first10 = Lynne A. | last11 = Hinkley | first11 = Sasha | last12 = Carpenter | first12 = John M. | last13 = Brewer | first13 = John M. | title = The Dynamical Mass and Three-Dimensional Orbit of HR7672B: A Benchmark Brown Dwarf with High Eccentricity | journal = [[天文物理期刊|The Astrophysical Journal]] | volume = 751 | issue = 2 | id = 97 | page = 14 | year = 2012 | arxiv = 1112.1725 | bibcode = 2012ApJ...751...97C | doi = 10.1088/0004-637X/751/2/97}}</ref>

=== 深空天体 ===
银河系螺旋带及其中的[[大裂縫_(天文學)|大裂缝]]经过天箭座，左旗一、左旗二和左旗增一标出大裂缝的边界<ref name="crossen 2004">{{cite book | last1 = Crossen | first1 = Craig | last2 = Rhemann | first2 = Gerald | title = Sky Vistas: Astronomy for Binoculars and Richest-Field Telescopes | publisher = Springer | location = New York | origyear = 2004 | year = 2012 | page = 150 | isbn = 978-3-709-10626-6 | access-date = 2020-11-29 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=3vELBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA150&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | archive-date = 2020-12-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201209091602/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=3vELBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA150&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。左旗二和左旗五之间的[[M71|M71]]<ref name="moore366" />是非常松散的[[球狀星團|球狀星團]]，人类曾误以为是密集的[[疏散星团|疏散星团]]<ref name="tt" />。法国天文学家[[让·菲利普·洛伊斯·德·谢索|让·菲利普·洛伊斯·德·谢索]]（{{lang|fr|Philippe Loys de Chéseaux}}）1745或1746年率先发现M71<ref name="tt">{{cite book | last1 = Thompson | first1 = Robert Bruce | last2 = Thompson | first2 = Barbara Fritchman | year = 2007 | title = Illustrated Guide to Astronomical Wonders: From Novice to Master Observer | page = 394 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=ymt9nj_uPhwC&pg=PA394&redir_esc=y | publisher = [[歐萊禮媒體|O'Reilly Media]] | location = North Sebastopol, California | access-date = 2020-11-29 | isbn = 978-0-596-52685-6 | archive-date = 2020-12-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201208180944/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=ymt9nj_uPhwC&pg=PA394&redir_esc=y | dead-url = no }}</ref>，距地球约1.3万光年<ref name="inglis2017">{{cite book | last = Inglis | first = Mike | title = Astronomy of the Milky Way: The Observer's Guide to the Northern Sky | year = 2017 | publisher = Springer | location = New York | isbn = 978-3-319-49082-3 | pages = 83–89 | access-date = 2020-11-29 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=02DTDgAAQBAJ&q=Messier+71&pg=PA89&redir_esc=y#v=snippet&q=Messier%2071&f=false | archive-date = 2020-12-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201208215629/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=02DTDgAAQBAJ&q=Messier+71&pg=PA89&redir_esc=y#v=snippet&q=Messier%2071&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

天箭座有两个著名行星状星云，[[NGC_6886|NGC 6886]]中心是结束漸近巨星支的高温恒星，质量约为太阳的五成五，光度2,700±850倍，表面温度14.2万K，周边星云估计已经膨胀1280至1600年<ref name="schonberner">{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/201731788 | bibcode = 2018A&A...609A.126S | title = Expansion patterns and parallaxes for planetary nebulae | year = 2018 | last1 = Schönberner | first1 = D. | last2 = Balick | first2 = B. | last3 = Jacob | first3 = R. | journal = Astronomy & Astrophysics | volume = 609 | page = A126}}</ref>。[[項鍊星雲|項鍊星雲]]本是近距离联星，其中一星扩张成巨星并将另一星吞没。偏小的星仍在巨星内部绕轨道旋转，而且自转速度大幅提升，导致外层物质受离心力影响向太空散发，团状恒星物质形成明亮的气体，进而组成环状星云。<ref name="NASANN">{{cite press release | last1 = Weaver | first1 = Donna | first2 = Ray | last2 = Villard | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112025406/http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/hubble/science/necklace-nebula.html | archivedate = 2020-11-12 | deadurl = no | date = 2011-08-11 | title = Hubble Offers a Dazzling 'Necklace' | url = https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/hubble/science/necklace-nebula.html | publisher = NASA | agency = Space Telescope Science Institute | access-date = 2020-11-29 }}</ref>两个星云与地球的距离都在1.5万光年左右<ref name="schonberner" /><ref name="NASANN" />。

